{"tid":847534,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[求意見]屋企個b playgroup遇到大陸惡b","createTime":"2018-10-04T08:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T02:14:26.000Z","uid":180913,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"38af35bcbe1227865501f8ae5647e63949f91dbd","tid":847534,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"我屋企有個 1歲9個月大bb<br />\n佢仲未好識講野，明人講咩會做動作咁上下<br />\n佢試過俾個大陸b一野衝埋有心撞佢 （撞中就實頭流血）同搶佢野<br />\n之後放學係咁拍心口話驚驚向大人<br />\n咁我最近放工就返去抱佢問佢返學點<br />\n佢即刻大叫 之後做咗喊嘅動作 最後叫媽媽<br />\n我阿媽解釋佢幾次放學 都喊<br />\n喊完搵大人<br />\n我本身想入去陪佢保護佢<br />\n但可惜playgroup唔俾大人入<br />\n<br />\n我 好擔心， 又唔知入面發生緊咩事<br />\n好在佢沖涼嗰陣時有冇啲咩表面傷痕<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以俾下意見<br />\n唔想教佢逃避囉但又唔知點樣教<br />\n<br />\n又擔心佢受到傷害<br />\n一陣驚咗返學都唔知點算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d78b15e6e7b7f263cd61f26c15a98df237bd48","tid":847534,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"惡魔的後裔"},{"pid":"b819849057239a13e8f3910976dd0759addd8557","tid":847534,"uid":52299,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"轉去第二度playgroup 咪得囉"},{"pid":"9eff217fe8ed960ee0195cecf1706e4ca852a5c6","tid":847534,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"b819849057239a13e8f3910976dd0759addd8557","tid":847534,"uid":52299,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"轉去第二度playgroup 咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"俾哂錢<br />\n屋企人想教佢面對多過想退<br />\n始終住係 雙非問題好嚴重既地區<br />\n上playgroup想提早適應"},{"pid":"60496183c32a63efef0197f8a9d14b6572af1096","tid":847534,"uid":177089,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"9eff217fe8ed960ee0195cecf1706e4ca852a5c6","tid":847534,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"b819849057239a13e8f3910976dd0759addd8557","tid":847534,"uid":52299,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T